Class Blocks

  • java.lang.Object
    • Blocks
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Blocks>
    class Blocks
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Blocks>
    Blocks.java version 0.1 will create Ethereum Blocks with simple methods. 1.0 version is create a blockchain and to have a foundation of fully function block chains. 2.0 version include timestamp and transactions. The file have method find different timestamp and transactions between two blocks. 3.0 version include Transactions variable to keep track a list of transactions for each blocks.
    Version:
    3.0
    Author:
    lyont
